= Changelog for chared =

== v1.2.1 (3 Jan 2013) ==
 * BUGFIX: Opening encoding models in the binary mode.

== v1.2 (23 Sep 2011) ==
 * FEATURE: Removed normalization of model vectors since it doesn't affect
            results in any way. This enabled making the stored models smaller. 

== v1.1 (1 Aug 2011) ==
 * FEATURE: Models based on n-grams of characters (trigrams by default).
 * FEATURE: More useful output when testing multiple documents.
 * FEATURE: Confusion matrix can be printed when learning new models. 

== v1.0 (24 Apr 2011) ==
 * First public release.
